      "sourceUrl": "https://github.com/doocs/leetcode/blob/main/solution/0600-0699/0645.Set%20Mismatch/README_EN.md",
      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    vector<int> findErrorNums(vector<int>& nums) {\n        int n = nums.size();\n        unordered_map<int, int> cnt;\n        for (int x : nums) {\n            ++cnt[x];\n        }\n        vector<int> ans(2);\n        for (int x = 1; x <= n; ++x) {\n            if (cnt[x] == 2) {\n                ans[0] = x;\n            } else if (cnt[x] == 0) {\n                ans[1] = x;\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n};"
