      "sourceUrl": "https://github.com/doocs/leetcode/blob/main/solution/0700-0799/0713.Subarray%20Product%20Less%20Than%20K/README.md",
      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    int numSubarrayProductLessThanK(vector<int>& nums, int k) {\n        int ans = 0, l = 0;\n        int p = 1;\n        for (int r = 0; r < nums.size(); ++r) {\n            p *= nums[r];\n            while (l <= r && p >= k) {\n                p /= nums[l++];\n            }\n            ans += r - l + 1;\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n};"
