      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    vector<int> constructArray(int n, int k) {\n        int l = 1, r = n;\n        vector<int> ans(n);\n        for (int i = 0; i < k; ++i) {\n            ans[i] = i % 2 == 0 ? l++ : r--;\n        }\n        for (int i = k; i < n; ++i) {\n            ans[i] = k % 2 == 0 ? r-- : l++;\n        }\n        return ans;\n    }\n};"
