      "code": "// The rand7() API is already defined for you.\n// int rand7();\n// @return a random integer in the range 1 to 7\n\nclass Solution {\npublic:\n    int rand10() {\n        while (1) {\n            int i = rand7() - 1;\n            int j = rand7();\n            int x = i * 7 + j;\n            if (x <= 40) {\n                return x % 10 + 1;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n};"
