      "sourceUrl": "https://github.com/doocs/leetcode/blob/main/solution/0000-0099/0096.Unique%20Binary%20Search%20Trees/README.md",
      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    int numTrees(int n) {\n        vector<int> f(n + 1);\n        f[0] = 1;\n        for (int i = 1; i <= n; ++i) {\n            for (int j = 0; j < i; ++j) {\n                f[i] += f[j] * f[i - j - 1];\n            }\n        }\n        return f[n];\n    }\n};"
