      "sourceUrl": "https://github.com/doocs/leetcode/blob/main/solution/1100-1199/1137.N-th%20Tribonacci%20Number/README.md",
      "code": "class Solution {\npublic:\n    int tribonacci(int n) {\n        long long a = 0, b = 1, c = 1;\n        while (n--) {\n            long long d = a + b + c;\n            a = b;\n            b = c;\n            c = d;\n        }\n        return (int) a;\n    }\n};"
